WEBVTT

01:39.509 --> 01:43.759
[Road to Success]

01:44.620 --> 01:47.820
[Episode 2]

01:56.039 --> 01:57.120
The school's official website is

01:56.979 --> 01:57.320
[Pay attention to mental growth]

01:57.120 --> 01:59.180
full of punishment notices about them.

01:57.370 --> 02:04.620
[School Bulletin Board]

01:59.430 --> 02:02.430
Their grades are basically
at the bottom of the class as well.

02:02.430 --> 02:04.150
No honors,

02:04.150 --> 02:06.230
and no shot at competitions.

02:07.510 --> 02:09.120
It seems that this time,

02:09.120 --> 02:11.760
it's really just going to be
a one-round tour for show.

02:11.760 --> 02:14.000
Let me just meet them openly.

02:25.960 --> 02:26.890
Hello, teacher.

02:27.110 --> 02:29.000
[Fu Xinshu,
former captain of the football team]

02:27.590 --> 02:29.390
Are you the new team supervisor?

02:29.590 --> 02:31.030
Yes, my surname is Lin.

02:32.120 --> 02:33.150
Hello, Ms. Lin.

02:33.590 --> 02:34.680
My name is Fu Xinshu.

02:34.680 --> 02:36.070
"Ms. Lin"?

02:36.150 --> 02:37.360
I've already told them to hurry up.

02:37.360 --> 02:38.360
They should be here soon.

02:38.360 --> 02:39.430
I bought you guys some milk tea.

02:39.430 --> 02:40.620
You can distribute it later.

02:40.620 --> 02:42.150
Okay, thank you, Ms. Lin.

02:44.840 --> 02:45.520
Fu Xinshu.

02:47.150 --> 02:48.750
Were you also on the football team before?

02:48.750 --> 02:49.560
Yes.

02:49.890 --> 02:50.750
What position?

02:51.400 --> 02:52.730
I used to play midfield.

02:53.800 --> 02:54.980
"Used to"?

02:55.010 --> 02:56.010
What about now?

02:58.030 --> 03:00.560
I haven't played football
for a long time now.

03:13.710 --> 03:14.710
Wen Chengye!

03:15.400 --> 03:16.870
So he's Wen Chengye.

03:18.360 --> 03:20.390
[Wen Chengye,
defender of the new football team]

03:19.400 --> 03:20.190
You know me?

03:20.470 --> 03:22.030
You're the transfer student from Class 4.

03:22.030 --> 03:24.560
You and your skateboard are
both very famous.

04:06.470 --> 04:08.270
Ms. Lin, I'll go rush them again.

04:08.670 --> 04:09.670
Hurry up. Come on.

04:10.150 --> 04:11.190
Wen Chengye?

04:13.800 --> 04:16.000
What? Are you here for the meeting, too?

04:16.519 --> 04:17.519
Wen Chengye.

04:20.399 --> 04:22.000
Please stay for the meeting.

04:26.720 --> 04:28.510
-Who does he think he is?
-Who cares about him?

04:28.510 --> 04:30.120
-Just ignore him, Boss.
-Yeah.

04:30.120 --> 04:31.120
Teacher?

04:31.920 --> 04:33.240
It's you!

04:36.430 --> 04:37.920
There's milk tea!

04:37.920 --> 04:38.680
-Teacher,
-How come it's her?

04:38.680 --> 04:40.560
you bought the milk tea, didn't you?

04:40.560 --> 04:41.560
Come and enjoy it.

04:41.950 --> 04:42.560
Okay!

04:44.630 --> 04:45.690
Boss, here you are.

04:49.430 --> 04:50.920
The teacher even bought us milk tea.

04:50.920 --> 04:52.310
She bought us milk tea.

04:52.310 --> 04:54.570
The new teacher is so beautiful and kind.

04:56.159 --> 04:57.870
-Fu!
-There's milk tea for us!

04:57.870 --> 05:00.510
How come you guys arrived
even later than us?

05:00.510 --> 05:02.510
-So what?
-So what, bro?

05:02.510 --> 05:03.720
Feng Suo, the teacher said

05:03.190 --> 05:04.620
[Name: Yu Ming]
[Name: Zheng Feiyang] [Name: Feng Suo]

05:03.720 --> 05:05.190
there's no milk tea
for those who are late.

05:05.190 --> 05:07.560
-We will... We will drink it anyway.
-Bro.

05:06.340 --> 05:07.440
[Feng Suo,
former goalkeeper of the football team]

05:07.560 --> 05:09.630
Master Zhi Hui was
the last one to get here,

05:07.610 --> 05:07.990
[Zheng Feiyang,
former defender of the football team]

05:08.010 --> 05:08.700
[Zheng Ren, former midfield player
of the football team]]

05:09.630 --> 05:11.120
not me, right?

05:10.770 --> 05:12.230
[Zhi Hui, former midfield player
of the football team]

05:12.720 --> 05:13.550
Master,

05:13.720 --> 05:15.560
which direction is lucky today?

05:16.950 --> 05:18.390
Anyway,

05:18.950 --> 05:21.120
it's not your position, Zheng Ren.

05:23.160 --> 05:23.630
Mr. Zhi Hui,

05:23.630 --> 05:25.430
how about here? How about my position?

05:25.430 --> 05:26.070
Not good, either.

05:26.070 --> 05:27.160
Yours is surely not...

05:27.160 --> 05:28.750
It's definitely not your position.

05:28.750 --> 05:29.430
It must be me,

05:29.430 --> 05:29.950
the chosen one.

05:29.950 --> 05:31.190
I'm sure it's not you.

05:32.120 --> 05:33.920
There he goes again, the Master.

05:34.159 --> 05:35.159
A one-round tour is guaranteed.

05:35.159 --> 05:35.920
All right, enough.

05:35.920 --> 05:37.520
Here's our team supervisor.

05:38.190 --> 05:40.070
Ms. Lin, everyone is here...

05:40.630 --> 05:41.960
except for Wen Chengye.

05:45.610 --> 05:47.040
Here, I'm announcing something.

05:47.040 --> 05:51.040
The school is arranging for you guys
to participate in a football match.

05:51.270 --> 05:53.310
I will serve
as your temporary team supervisor.

05:53.310 --> 05:54.310
My surname is Lin.

05:54.800 --> 05:55.600
Football match?

05:55.600 --> 05:57.070
At 2:30 PM this Sunday,

05:57.070 --> 05:59.750
let's meet at the school gate to play...

06:02.950 --> 06:04.870
in the Youth Super League qualifiers.

06:04.870 --> 06:06.430
Our rival is Ning'an Experimental School.

06:06.430 --> 06:08.000
Ning'an Experimental School's team is
super strong.

06:08.000 --> 06:09.360
We definitely can't beat them.

06:09.360 --> 06:10.950
How about we forfeit again?

06:10.950 --> 06:12.000
Yeah, let's forfeit.

06:12.000 --> 06:13.730
We haven't trained for 2 years.

06:13.750 --> 06:14.480
What are we going for?

06:14.480 --> 06:15.360
Exactly.

06:15.750 --> 06:16.980
To make a fool of ourselves?

06:16.980 --> 06:19.430
Our football team has been disbanded
for so long.

06:19.430 --> 06:21.360
Why are we still playing?

06:21.360 --> 06:22.180
Yeah, why?

06:22.210 --> 06:24.340
-Play for what?
-I'm not going anyway.

06:24.870 --> 06:26.920
They all seem very negative.

06:27.240 --> 06:29.700
Those who don't show up will fail PE,

06:29.870 --> 06:30.990
and we'll notify your parents.

06:30.990 --> 06:32.230
I'll take down the names.

06:32.230 --> 06:35.230
Ms. Lin, you probably
don't have that right, I think?

06:35.260 --> 06:37.120
Director Qian gave me this right.

06:38.420 --> 06:39.250
Fu Xinshu,

06:39.430 --> 06:41.159
have everyone sign this later.

06:45.070 --> 06:48.040
Fu, we've already shown you respect.

06:49.100 --> 06:50.050
-Goodbye.
-Bye-bye.

06:50.050 --> 06:50.880
Bye-bye.

07:01.120 --> 07:01.960
Ms. Lin,

07:02.750 --> 07:05.000
they don't care about failing,

07:05.630 --> 07:07.890
because they fail almost every subject.

07:08.430 --> 07:10.690
But I'll try my best
to get them all there.

07:12.000 --> 07:12.840
Thank you.

07:16.950 --> 07:18.750
Boss, are we really not
playing that match?

07:17.840 --> 07:21.330
[Fight for your youth!]

07:20.270 --> 07:22.190
The team was easily disbanded back then.

07:22.190 --> 07:23.630
Now they want me back?

07:24.160 --> 07:25.490
What do they take me for?

07:25.820 --> 07:28.500
That's true, but...

07:39.870 --> 07:41.130
Did you buy this for me?

07:42.630 --> 07:44.290
It definitely wasn't from me.

07:51.300 --> 07:52.070
Could it...

07:52.630 --> 07:54.310
be from Xiaotian?

07:54.310 --> 07:57.510
The Class Beauty wouldn't have
such bad taste, would she?

08:00.510 --> 08:02.070
Bao Xiaotian has good taste,

08:02.070 --> 08:03.630
having taken a liking to you, Boss.

08:03.630 --> 08:05.560
Lin Lu, did you just call me?

08:10.510 --> 08:11.310
Bao Xiaotian,

08:11.750 --> 08:13.280
what do you think of my boss?

08:29.830 --> 08:31.490
I don't know him at all.

08:35.309 --> 08:37.770
There's a second way
to solve this question.

08:38.630 --> 08:40.090
Can you stop being so nosy?

08:40.840 --> 08:43.360
Don't you know girls are
easily embarrassed?

08:43.360 --> 08:44.630
My bad, my bad.

08:46.200 --> 08:47.080
Open it and see.

08:49.600 --> 08:50.530
What do you think

08:50.690 --> 08:51.930
she got me as a gift?

08:56.080 --> 08:58.870
Are you sure it's from her?

08:59.510 --> 09:00.710
Why wouldn't it be?

09:00.790 --> 09:02.920
-Do you have a death wish?
-Okay, fine.

09:03.200 --> 09:03.940
Chocolate?

09:03.960 --> 09:04.750
And a note.

09:17.900 --> 09:18.920
Ms. Lin,

09:18.940 --> 09:20.070
what does this mean?

09:20.320 --> 09:22.650
It was definitely you who did this, right?

09:25.810 --> 09:29.220
Do you feel uncertain about your life?

09:29.250 --> 09:31.500
Do you still not know
where your future is heading?

09:31.500 --> 09:33.900
Lin of No. 8 High School
specializes in treating

09:33.900 --> 09:37.430
school refusal, truancy,
lack of motivation, and poor grades.

09:44.840 --> 09:45.970
Did you do this, too?

09:46.550 --> 09:48.230
You really love playing pranks, Ms. Lin.

09:47.810 --> 09:48.700
[100 free football equipment rentals]

09:48.260 --> 09:49.140
Childish.

09:49.170 --> 09:51.230
Not only did you give me a little gift,

09:51.370 --> 09:53.150
but you also gave one to Chen Jianghe?

09:53.150 --> 09:54.390
And you, bro.

09:54.390 --> 09:56.240
You actually believed it? You're so naive.

09:56.240 --> 09:57.200
I started working here

09:57.200 --> 09:59.800
this Monday, September 2nd,
for the first day.

10:00.200 --> 10:01.600
You registered last week,

10:01.600 --> 10:02.730
before I even got here.

10:02.730 --> 10:03.530
Furthermore,

10:04.960 --> 10:06.160
where did you find it?

10:07.360 --> 10:08.170
In my desk drawer.

10:08.170 --> 10:10.370
Then tell me, my dear student, Qin Ao.

10:10.600 --> 10:12.010
In broad daylight,

10:12.080 --> 10:13.360
how did I go hide this chocolate

10:13.360 --> 10:15.560
in your desk drawer without being seen?

10:16.480 --> 10:18.080
It was computer class this morning.

10:18.080 --> 10:20.210
So you could sneak into the classroom.

10:20.510 --> 10:22.240
Besides, you just look like a student.

10:22.240 --> 10:23.150
Thank you.

10:23.150 --> 10:24.510
But I'm not into that.

10:25.320 --> 10:26.300
I

10:26.370 --> 10:28.510
graduated with a master's degree
from Yongchuan University.

10:28.510 --> 10:30.280
I was our province's top liberal arts scorer
in the college entrance exam.

10:30.280 --> 10:32.510
I have published 6 SCI papers in total—

10:32.600 --> 10:34.170
4 as the first author.

10:34.200 --> 10:36.350
I've received first-class scholarships
for 7 years.

10:36.350 --> 10:38.880
If I hadn't wanted to live a life
of just getting by,

10:38.880 --> 10:41.010
why would I have ended up sitting here?

10:41.360 --> 10:42.230
Ms. Lin,

10:42.330 --> 10:44.930
isn't it inappropriate for you
to brag so much?

10:45.030 --> 10:46.720
Ms. Lin, was it really not you?

10:53.000 --> 10:54.930
Then why is your phone number on it?

10:55.550 --> 10:56.790
It also asks us to come to you.

10:56.790 --> 10:57.720
It must have something to do with you.

10:57.720 --> 10:58.690
Think it over again, Ms. Lin.

10:58.690 --> 11:00.950
Boss, let's go over there to check it out.

11:04.360 --> 11:06.120
There's a note
in every piece of chocolate.

11:06.120 --> 11:07.600
What are these? I don't understand.

11:07.600 --> 11:09.330
Nine of them have words on them.

11:09.750 --> 11:11.410
Why doesn't this one have any?

11:15.850 --> 11:16.850
How should I know?

11:19.480 --> 11:20.480
Ms. Lin,

11:20.870 --> 11:22.360
aren't you a master's graduate

11:22.360 --> 11:24.360
from Yongchuan University,

11:24.360 --> 11:26.550
the province's top liberal arts scorer
in the college entrance exam,

11:26.550 --> 11:28.080
and a straight-A student who wrote

11:28.080 --> 11:30.690
some SOS papers?

11:30.870 --> 11:31.910
You should know, right?

11:31.910 --> 11:33.840
It's "SCI."

11:34.510 --> 11:35.960
I know.

11:37.440 --> 11:40.040
The straight-A student
can't even solve this?

11:42.720 --> 11:44.510
If I can't solve a puzzle,

11:44.510 --> 11:46.710
there could only be two possibilities.

11:46.910 --> 11:49.720
Firstly, it's not a puzzle at all.

11:49.720 --> 11:52.200
Secondly, I don't
want to solve it for now.

11:55.640 --> 11:57.210
Each sentence has a different length.

11:56.360 --> 11:57.090
[100 free football equipment rentals]

11:57.240 --> 11:58.870
There is a repeated word.

12:00.240 --> 12:01.750
Is it a crossword puzzle?

12:02.580 --> 12:03.440
[Diligence makes up for a lack of talent]
[Hard work makes the door to success]

12:03.600 --> 12:04.360
Okay.

12:05.390 --> 12:07.320
The grid for puzzle solving.

12:07.670 --> 12:08.390
Got it.

12:07.970 --> 12:10.320
[Hints about the poems]

12:12.390 --> 12:13.540
[Diligence makes up for a lack of talent]
[Hard work makes the door to success]

12:15.880 --> 12:17.030
Ms. Lin,

12:17.050 --> 12:18.810
have you found anything?

12:19.250 --> 12:20.800
[Make a great coup]

12:25.300 --> 12:27.510
[Start over again] [Dreams come true]

12:31.440 --> 12:34.790
"Xin-shu."

12:32.960 --> 12:35.440
[Stay calm] [Dreams come true]

12:37.110 --> 12:38.370
Which word do you think

12:39.930 --> 12:41.650
should be filled in the front?

12:41.680 --> 12:43.250
Isn't that self-evident?

12:43.720 --> 12:44.670
It must be...

12:45.040 --> 12:45.840
-"Fu."
-"Fu."

12:51.590 --> 12:52.790
What brings you here?

12:55.060 --> 12:55.940
Hello, Ms. Lin.

12:57.270 --> 12:58.090
What's up?

13:00.720 --> 13:02.080
Did you guys change your mind

13:02.080 --> 13:03.360
and decide to play
in the match this weekend?

13:03.360 --> 13:04.390
No way!

13:04.390 --> 13:06.150
Bro, it's daytime.

13:06.150 --> 13:07.080
Wake up, please.

13:07.080 --> 13:08.790
I don't play meaningless matches.

13:08.790 --> 13:09.920
We can't win anyway.

13:10.870 --> 13:11.720
I know.

13:13.390 --> 13:14.030
But what if I

13:14.030 --> 13:15.830
still want to invite you to play?

13:15.960 --> 13:17.490
Let's get down to business.

13:18.360 --> 13:19.960
Someone played a prank on me.

13:22.320 --> 13:22.960
Simply put,

13:22.960 --> 13:24.550
someone gave us a puzzle,

13:24.550 --> 13:26.030
a crossword puzzle.

13:26.030 --> 13:28.720
And this is our deduction process.

13:28.720 --> 13:31.000
We've deduced
that your name goes in this blank.

13:29.680 --> 13:31.370
[Start over again] [Make a great coup]

13:33.200 --> 13:35.600
-"Xinshu."
-You are the one related

13:35.600 --> 13:37.290
to Ms. Lin and us.

13:37.310 --> 13:38.550
So the answer must be you.

13:38.550 --> 13:39.600
Why me?

13:39.600 --> 13:40.320
Even though he's

13:40.320 --> 13:42.630
-the one who wants to play the most...
-We also inferred it from this hint...

13:42.630 --> 13:43.790
Did you receive anything similar?

13:43.790 --> 13:45.870
Judging from his reaction,

13:46.820 --> 13:48.440
he didn't do this.

13:50.440 --> 13:51.540
My brain hurts.

13:51.840 --> 13:54.080
Let's go. Time to go home for dinner.

13:54.610 --> 13:55.780
I remember now.

13:58.000 --> 13:59.080
I did receive something.

13:59.080 --> 13:59.960
Really?

14:00.410 --> 14:01.290
What is it?

14:04.360 --> 14:06.200
I'll tell you if you come to play

14:06.480 --> 14:07.550
in the match this weekend.

14:07.550 --> 14:08.200
Hold on.

14:09.890 --> 14:11.320
You're still one player short

14:11.320 --> 14:12.790
for the team, right?

14:14.000 --> 14:15.000
I'll handle it.

14:23.270 --> 14:25.690
[Hongjing No. 8 High School]

14:25.780 --> 14:30.150
[Administrative Building]

14:34.870 --> 14:37.390
I don't know how to do the homework
the teacher assigned last time.

14:37.390 --> 14:40.120
Same here.
I've been looking it up for a long time.

14:51.270 --> 14:52.130
Wen Chengye...

14:56.030 --> 14:56.960
What do you want from me?

14:56.960 --> 14:57.790
Just say it.

14:59.030 --> 14:59.840
You left early today,

14:59.840 --> 15:00.870
so you didn't hear it.

15:00.870 --> 15:02.000
This Sunday afternoon at 2:30,

15:02.000 --> 15:03.510
we'll meet at the school gate
for the match.

15:03.510 --> 15:04.440
Can you join us?

15:08.940 --> 15:10.400
You've waited for so long.

15:10.440 --> 15:11.920
Is this very important to you?

15:11.920 --> 15:12.850
Very important.

15:13.390 --> 15:14.910
Ever since the team disbanded,

15:14.910 --> 15:16.030
what I want to do most is

15:16.030 --> 15:18.430
to play football with everyone once again.

15:19.240 --> 15:21.770
I also hope you can join us
as our new teammate.

15:30.510 --> 15:31.390
Okay.

15:31.790 --> 15:32.920
I will definitely go

15:33.120 --> 15:34.180
and arrive on time.

15:58.840 --> 15:59.960
The lights are off?

16:16.120 --> 16:17.390
So he is home.

16:18.840 --> 16:19.750
No way,

16:19.750 --> 16:21.240
is he bathing in the dark?

16:21.640 --> 16:23.700
Or did he forget to turn off the water?

16:34.780 --> 16:36.620
This guy is too weird.

16:45.370 --> 16:46.330
Hello,

16:46.750 --> 16:47.550
I'd like to know

16:47.550 --> 16:49.510
about the new tenant upstairs.

16:51.720 --> 16:53.600
I know he pays a lot of rent,

16:53.600 --> 16:54.600
but I still need to know

16:54.600 --> 16:56.330
his basic information, right?

16:58.000 --> 16:59.200
If he's really that rich,

16:59.200 --> 17:00.840
why didn't he rent a luxury apartment?

17:00.840 --> 17:04.119
Just because he's handsome
doesn't mean he's a good person.

17:04.119 --> 17:05.790
Come on, sir.

17:05.790 --> 17:07.869
Just think it over.
I'm not joking with you.

17:07.869 --> 17:09.109
Installing a bathtub in the living room

17:09.109 --> 17:10.310
of this old residential building

17:10.310 --> 17:11.349
and bathing in the dark—

17:11.349 --> 17:12.829
don't you think it's so weird?

17:12.829 --> 17:15.270
What if he's some psycho killer?

17:15.270 --> 17:18.400
Think about how dangerous it is
for me to live here alone.

17:20.400 --> 17:21.109
Okay.

17:21.790 --> 17:24.990
Please make sure
you investigate this thoroughly for me.

17:41.200 --> 17:42.350
You're still up now?

17:43.860 --> 17:45.290
It's only 9 o'clock.

17:49.240 --> 17:50.550
Um,

17:51.030 --> 17:53.230
since when have you been standing here?

17:54.210 --> 17:54.970
Not long ago.

17:56.200 --> 17:58.460
Just since you started making that call.

18:04.480 --> 18:05.400
That's great.

18:07.270 --> 18:09.440
I'm used to sleeping early
and waking up early.

18:09.440 --> 18:11.790
Then I'll get in now.

18:11.790 --> 18:14.000
I am 30 years old,

18:14.000 --> 18:15.960
from Yongchuan, unemployed.

18:20.570 --> 18:21.350
Good night,

18:21.910 --> 18:22.910
Miss Landlady.

18:24.590 --> 18:26.550
I don't want to kill you yet.

18:39.000 --> 18:41.060
I've only been at work for 2 days,

18:41.240 --> 18:43.570
and I've already received 2 little gifts.

18:45.640 --> 18:47.150
A football lending card.

18:47.350 --> 18:48.860
A little note.

18:49.880 --> 18:53.410
I was also asked to rebuild
the football team as the supervisor.

18:55.160 --> 18:57.480
Who on earth is messing with me,

18:58.070 --> 18:59.750
and why?

19:05.790 --> 19:08.060
And the QR Code upstairs

19:08.680 --> 19:10.350
is also weird.

19:17.480 --> 19:19.720
Is there any connection

19:20.350 --> 19:22.400
between them?

19:32.640 --> 19:34.350
Do you have any idea?

19:52.750 --> 19:54.210
Out for a morning workout?

19:55.810 --> 19:57.240
You got the pancakes from this restaurant?

19:57.240 --> 19:58.770
The line is usually super long.

19:58.770 --> 20:00.100
They are freshly baked.

20:00.110 --> 20:00.790
Try some?

20:01.930 --> 20:03.790
No, thanks. I have a match to go to.

20:18.920 --> 20:21.050
We still don't have everyone here yet.

20:21.550 --> 20:22.310
Come on...

20:23.440 --> 20:25.750
Even though I don't want to play,
I still arrived early.

20:25.750 --> 20:28.200
In view of this pre-match gathering alone,

20:28.300 --> 20:30.360
you can already tell today's match is

20:30.550 --> 20:31.410
looking rough.

20:34.330 --> 20:35.980
Are you giving up already?

20:36.480 --> 20:38.590
What? We're obviously going to lose.

20:38.960 --> 20:40.390
Watch your mouth.

20:40.760 --> 20:41.840
I'm in the team.

20:42.070 --> 20:45.530
I once dribbled past 5 players in a row
and scored with one kick.

20:46.000 --> 20:46.880
And now?

20:47.350 --> 20:48.510
You pant after running 2 laps.

20:48.510 --> 20:50.270
A true hero doesn't boast of past glory.

20:50.270 --> 20:52.340
-I mean, I can still do it now, okay?
-Keep bragging.

20:52.340 --> 20:54.730
Ms. Lin, is there no milk tea today?

21:01.090 --> 21:02.400
Is everyone here?

21:10.030 --> 21:11.230
Where's Wen Chengye?

21:11.360 --> 21:14.030
[Everyone else is here
and waiting for you.Are you almost here?]

21:13.600 --> 21:14.400
Fu!

21:14.920 --> 21:17.350
Are you sure
Wen Chengye promised to come today?

21:17.350 --> 21:19.350
Is he too scared of losing to show up?

21:24.160 --> 21:26.550
"I'm not coming, you idiot"?

21:24.820 --> 21:25.860
[I'm not coming, you idiot.]

21:28.950 --> 21:30.390
It's fine, Fu.

21:30.550 --> 21:32.160
I... I'll get revenge for you later.

21:32.160 --> 21:33.310
Great.

21:33.310 --> 21:35.590
Ms. Lin, since Wen Chengye isn't coming,

21:35.590 --> 21:36.830
we don't even have enough players.

21:36.830 --> 21:38.560
Let's just disband right here.

21:43.680 --> 21:46.280
You've got a point.
I'll go tell Director Qian.

21:46.660 --> 21:48.310
It's time!
Why haven't you gotten on the bus?

21:48.310 --> 21:49.110
The match is about to start!

21:49.110 --> 21:50.590
Director Qian, here's the thing.

21:50.590 --> 21:52.640
Wen Chengye got held up
and couldn't make it.

21:52.640 --> 21:54.240
The team is one player short.

21:54.750 --> 21:57.350
Can we just not go?

21:57.350 --> 21:59.580
If he's not coming,
we'll find someone else!

21:59.580 --> 22:01.030
What do you mean by "not go"?

22:01.030 --> 22:03.440
The school leaders are
taking this very seriously today.

22:03.440 --> 22:05.200
How can you just forfeit easily?

22:05.200 --> 22:06.350
But we don't have enough players.

22:06.350 --> 22:08.350
Then let's figure it out!

22:09.400 --> 22:10.590
Don't pull a long face.

22:10.590 --> 22:11.920
It's my treat today!

22:11.920 --> 22:13.450
Come on, have some goodies.

22:13.590 --> 22:15.510
Don't pull a long face. Give me a smile.

22:15.510 --> 22:17.110
I bought some snacks for you.

22:17.110 --> 22:18.440
You're usually so cute.

22:19.720 --> 22:20.780
Don't look so down.

22:22.030 --> 22:24.160
You usually have the brightest smile.

22:24.240 --> 22:25.440
Come on, here you are.

22:25.440 --> 22:26.830
Come on, come on!

22:26.830 --> 22:28.090
-Thank you, Director.
-Thank you, Director.

22:28.090 --> 22:30.620
-Thank you, Director.
-Thank you, Director.

22:31.310 --> 22:32.790
Thank you, Director.

22:34.510 --> 22:35.370
Here's for you.

22:36.310 --> 22:38.180
Don't worry, just go ahead.

22:38.240 --> 22:40.000
Leave this matter to me.

22:40.000 --> 22:42.350
I promise before you even arrive,

22:42.350 --> 22:45.350
the substitute will already be
waiting there for you.

22:45.480 --> 22:46.400
Take it.

22:47.210 --> 22:47.670
Get in the bus!

22:47.670 --> 22:48.410
Thank you.

22:48.440 --> 22:49.510
Hurry up! Stop dawdling!

22:49.510 --> 22:50.590
Stop messing around. Hurry!

22:50.590 --> 22:51.550
It's getting late!

22:51.550 --> 22:53.980
Go! Get moving! Get on the bus!

22:54.010 --> 22:55.400
Hurry up! Come on!

22:55.400 --> 22:56.590
Get on! Get on now!

23:22.000 --> 23:23.550
This bus is pretty fancy.

23:24.920 --> 23:26.400
And they're well-equipped.

23:26.400 --> 23:27.680
I'm so jealous.

23:28.440 --> 23:30.200
-Thank you, Coach.
-Thank you, Coach.

23:30.200 --> 23:31.330
-Hurry up!
-Come on!

23:31.550 --> 23:33.510
Their conditions are way too good.

23:34.110 --> 23:35.310
That's a bit too much.

23:35.720 --> 23:36.590
They're so delicate.

23:36.590 --> 23:37.270
Hurry up.

23:38.880 --> 23:39.810
Let me take this.

23:41.550 --> 23:43.410
Boss, I want this treatment, too.

23:45.160 --> 23:47.030
Then you should ask Ms. Lin for it.

23:48.030 --> 23:49.510
What supplies do we have?

23:51.280 --> 23:52.350
I ordered some water for you

23:52.350 --> 23:53.720
from a nearby farmhouse.

23:53.720 --> 23:54.450
Oh, God...

23:54.470 --> 23:56.440
Let's go.

23:56.440 --> 23:57.270
Here we are.

23:57.270 --> 23:58.200
Come on, get off.

23:58.790 --> 24:00.790
Relax and play well.

24:00.790 --> 24:01.880
-Okay!
-Okay.

24:02.350 --> 24:04.680
When did we get another football team?

24:05.240 --> 24:07.030
They came for the chemistry competition,

24:07.030 --> 24:08.590
taking the test
in the building over there.

24:08.590 --> 24:09.350
Chemistry has always been

24:09.350 --> 24:12.080
Hongjing's strongest subject
in competitions.

24:13.270 --> 24:14.160
I'm coming!

24:14.160 --> 24:16.510
Chen Weidong
from the track and field team?

24:16.510 --> 24:17.830
I came right after Director Qian

24:17.830 --> 24:18.640
talked to me.

24:18.640 --> 24:20.400
So everyone's here. Let's go.

24:20.640 --> 24:21.840
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

24:24.570 --> 24:29.170
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

24:28.760 --> 24:29.640
Stop there.

24:29.190 --> 24:33.610
[Hongjing No. 8 High School vs.
Ning'an Experimental School]

24:31.790 --> 24:33.830
Everyone, show your faces.

24:33.830 --> 24:36.510
Why bother taking photos
if it's going to be a one-round tour?

24:36.510 --> 24:38.000
She was probably
just completing a photo task

24:38.000 --> 24:39.530
assigned by Director Qian.

24:42.030 --> 24:43.270
Ms. Lin,

24:43.270 --> 24:44.270
can I really do it?

24:44.790 --> 24:45.680
Chen Weidong,

24:45.680 --> 24:46.680
we never thought about winning.

24:46.680 --> 24:48.400
Why are you taking it so seriously?

24:48.400 --> 24:50.160
Bro, Wen Chengye didn't come,

24:50.160 --> 24:51.240
but you did.

24:51.240 --> 24:52.710
You have my respect.

24:55.030 --> 24:56.400
Ning'an united,

24:56.400 --> 24:58.460
fighting only for the championship!

25:02.590 --> 25:05.680
Should we also come up
with a slogan together?

25:06.550 --> 25:08.150
What's there to think about?

25:08.160 --> 25:10.160
We're just here to run a few laps,

25:10.160 --> 25:12.110
lose the game, and put on a show.

25:12.110 --> 25:14.110
Then we have to put on a full show.

25:14.830 --> 25:15.640
Come on.

25:16.110 --> 25:17.710
Who can come up with a slogan?

25:18.350 --> 25:19.880
Qi Liang, let Qi Liang do it.

25:20.550 --> 25:21.350
Why don't you do it?

25:21.350 --> 25:23.010
Aren't you always talkative?

25:24.350 --> 25:25.810
Then I'll come up with one.

25:27.790 --> 25:30.400
Hongjing, Hongjing, shining stars!

25:31.510 --> 25:33.510
-That's so tacky.
-Oh...

25:37.550 --> 25:38.750
Then you think of one.

25:42.310 --> 25:43.200
Gather here.

25:43.200 --> 25:46.200
If you don't join me,
I'll tell Director Qian about it.

25:46.680 --> 25:47.790
There you go again,

25:47.790 --> 25:49.310
bringing up Director Qian.

25:49.310 --> 25:50.110
Come on.

25:51.920 --> 25:52.680
Director Qian.

25:52.680 --> 25:55.640
Hongjing, Hongjing, shining stars!

25:55.640 --> 25:58.440
-Hongjing, Hongjing...
-Hongjing, Hongjing...

25:59.110 --> 26:00.400
Say it louder.

26:01.510 --> 26:03.400
-Hongjing, Hongjing,
-Hongjing, Hongjing,

26:03.400 --> 26:05.350
-shining stars!
-shining stars!

26:08.200 --> 26:09.240
Let's go.

26:16.060 --> 26:17.440
Today's match is about to start.

26:16.340 --> 26:16.720
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

26:16.740 --> 26:17.270
[Hongjing No. 8 High School vs.
Ning'an Experimental School]

26:17.440 --> 26:18.400
The two teams are

26:18.400 --> 26:20.510
Ning'an Experimental School
and Hongjing No. 8 High School.

26:20.510 --> 26:21.750
The match officially begins.

26:21.750 --> 26:24.310
First up, there's a coin toss
to choose sides.

26:24.310 --> 26:27.000
The ones in blue and black striped uniforms
are from Ning'an Experimental School.

26:27.000 --> 26:28.720
Their team is extremely fast

26:28.720 --> 26:29.720
and known as the "Cheetahs."

26:29.720 --> 26:32.440
The team in the blue jerseys is
Hongjing No. 8 High School.

26:32.440 --> 26:34.960
They haven't participated
in any match for 2 years.

26:34.960 --> 26:36.310
In fact, just 2 months without playing

26:36.310 --> 26:37.750
can completely change a team.

26:37.750 --> 26:40.160
And they've been absent for 2 whole years.

26:40.160 --> 26:40.920
In the football fans' eyes,

26:40.920 --> 26:42.750
their chances of winning look slim.

26:42.750 --> 26:44.160
The 2 forwards
of Hongjing No. 8 High School

26:44.160 --> 26:45.550
are No. 9, Qin Ao,

26:45.550 --> 26:47.200
and No. 7, Chen Jianghe.

26:47.200 --> 26:47.790
Chen Jianghe is

26:47.790 --> 26:50.160
good at one-touch finishing in the box.

26:50.160 --> 26:50.830
As for Qin Ao,

26:50.830 --> 26:52.440
he's good at using changes of pace

26:52.440 --> 26:54.300
to pull off one-on-one dribbles.

26:54.920 --> 26:56.510
This is
Hongjing No. 8 High School's goalkeeper,

26:56.510 --> 26:57.400
No. 1, Feng Suo.

26:57.400 --> 26:59.920
He is the team's last line of defense.

26:59.920 --> 27:01.240
Hongjing's 2 core defenders

27:01.240 --> 27:03.400
are No. 6, Lin Lu, and No. 5, Yu Ming.

27:03.400 --> 27:04.920
Because of his small stature, Lin Lu was

27:04.920 --> 27:05.790
once jokingly called

27:05.790 --> 27:08.070
a player who'd jump up
and shatter your knees.

27:08.070 --> 27:09.200
Next to him is Yu Ming,

27:09.200 --> 27:10.880
capable of charging down the flanks.

27:10.880 --> 27:13.110
The 2 teams are making
their final pre-match preparations.

27:13.110 --> 27:14.030
I wonder if it's because the ones

27:14.030 --> 27:14.960
from Hongjing No. 8 High School

27:14.960 --> 27:16.160
haven't played for so long,

27:16.160 --> 27:17.350
but they look a bit loose.

27:17.350 --> 27:18.510
QR Code?

27:20.400 --> 27:21.640
What is he doing here?

27:24.070 --> 27:25.160
Come on! Go for it!

27:26.160 --> 27:27.160
Mark your men

27:27.510 --> 27:28.710
and watch the timing!

27:29.070 --> 27:30.000
Come on!

27:32.790 --> 27:34.070
The match begins!

27:34.070 --> 27:35.200
Ning'an Experimental School's team
kicks off.

27:35.200 --> 27:36.750
Their passing speed is very fast.

27:36.750 --> 27:38.750
Hongjing No. 8 High School
stands no chance

27:38.750 --> 27:39.960
to intercept the ball.

27:39.960 --> 27:41.550
The situation is instantly
under Ning'an Team's control.

27:41.550 --> 27:43.680
-Hongjing No. 8 High School's captain,
-Mark him!

27:43.680 --> 27:45.550
No. 10 Fu Xinshu,
is like Hongjing's midfield engine.

27:45.550 --> 27:47.070
He commands the team's defense

27:47.070 --> 27:49.830
and is the heart
of the entire Hongjing Team.

27:50.160 --> 27:52.110
I didn't expect to be
this fun participating

27:52.110 --> 27:53.720
in such a high school league.

27:54.310 --> 27:56.370
These kids aren't entirely useless.

27:58.340 --> 28:00.050
It's so passionate!

28:00.110 --> 28:02.000
This is their true battlefield.

28:02.550 --> 28:03.720
I suddenly feel that

28:03.720 --> 28:05.160
football is actually quite fun.

28:05.160 --> 28:06.160
Shoot!

28:08.720 --> 28:11.110
So fast? Has it even been a minute?

28:12.030 --> 28:13.440
They can't be this bad, right?

28:12.350 --> 28:14.700
[Ning'an Experimental School 01]
[Hongjing No. 8 High School 00]

28:16.680 --> 28:18.030
Goal! One to zero.

28:18.030 --> 28:19.790
Ning'an Experimental School
scored the first goal.

28:19.790 --> 28:21.400
The Hongjing No. 8 High School's players

28:21.400 --> 28:22.880
look nowhere near as good as before.

28:22.880 --> 28:24.350
During the 2 years they haven't competed,

28:24.350 --> 28:26.400
did they do nothing but sleep?

28:26.400 --> 28:27.720
Hongjing No. 8 High School is
in very poor form.

28:27.720 --> 28:28.790
After the goal,

28:28.790 --> 28:31.270
the team members
seem to have started blaming each other.

28:31.270 --> 28:33.880
No. 9 Qin Ao and No. 6 Lin Lu
miscommunicated.

28:33.880 --> 28:34.750
Yeah,

28:34.750 --> 28:35.880
there's still time!

28:35.880 --> 28:37.510
Go for it!

28:37.510 --> 28:39.350
-Captain Fu Xinshu is passing the ball.
-Watch the ball!

28:39.350 --> 28:40.920
But the ball has been intercepted!

28:40.920 --> 28:42.030
The ball!

28:43.790 --> 28:45.200
Ning'an shoots!

28:45.200 --> 28:47.270
The ball was saved by Feng Suo!

28:51.880 --> 28:54.590
The ball is once again
with Hongjing No. 8 High School.

28:54.590 --> 28:56.640
Number 9, Qin Ao,
with his individual skill,

28:56.640 --> 28:58.400
has dribbled the ball
into the penalty area.

28:58.400 --> 28:59.510
Shoot!

29:00.030 --> 29:03.000
Unfortunately, it was also saved
by Ning'an's goalkeeper.

29:03.000 --> 29:04.480
Both sides have exchanged
attacks and defenses,

29:04.480 --> 29:06.740
neither gaining an absolute advantage.

29:07.030 --> 29:08.270
The running speed of both teams' players

29:08.270 --> 29:10.160
has noticeably slowed down on the field.

29:10.160 --> 29:10.830
Lack of endurance

29:10.830 --> 29:12.830
has always been Ning'an's weakness.

29:12.830 --> 29:15.960
However, Hongjing Team has clearly
lacked training for 2 years,

29:15.960 --> 29:18.420
and their stamina is also
failing to keep up.

29:26.110 --> 29:27.640
Why is he still here?

29:28.380 --> 29:30.050
Could it be that he

29:30.080 --> 29:32.280
also likes watching football matches?

29:38.210 --> 29:39.870
You know about football, too?

29:41.350 --> 29:42.110
A little bit.

29:43.510 --> 29:44.370
Watch the game.

29:46.830 --> 29:49.550
Hongjing's No. 10 is advancing
at high speed with the ball.

29:49.550 --> 29:52.110
The 2 players collided for the ball,
and the ball was intercepted!

29:52.110 --> 29:52.830
They crashed into each other.

29:52.830 --> 29:54.000
Fu Xinshu was knocked down,

29:54.000 --> 29:55.730
falling heavily to the ground.

29:57.550 --> 29:58.510
The right side!

29:59.070 --> 30:02.720
Ning'an
dribbled past Hongjing's No. 5, Yu Ming.

30:03.200 --> 30:05.110
He's still advancing.

30:07.790 --> 30:09.880
Hongjing Team's No. 12
used his body to block,

30:09.880 --> 30:11.310
but the referee blew the whistle!

30:11.310 --> 30:13.480
-Looks like No. 12 committed a handball!
-Calm down, calm down.

30:13.480 --> 30:15.480
It was my shoulder that hit the ball.

30:18.030 --> 30:19.090
What's happening?

30:19.270 --> 30:20.160
The referee thinks

30:20.160 --> 30:21.510
your defending player

30:21.510 --> 30:23.440
opened his arms
in the opponent's penalty area,

30:23.440 --> 30:24.830
and his arm touched the ball,

30:24.830 --> 30:25.830
so a penalty kick was awarded.

30:25.830 --> 30:27.750
So did he actually commit a handball?

30:27.750 --> 30:29.350
From my angle,

30:29.380 --> 30:30.080
no.

30:31.880 --> 30:35.140
-What? Do that again, and you're off.
-Alright, it's okay.

30:35.590 --> 30:37.400
He even blew the whistle for that.

30:37.400 --> 30:38.680
Let's go.

30:39.310 --> 30:41.270
What should we do in this situation?

30:41.270 --> 30:43.110
This is the first lesson for you—

30:44.030 --> 30:45.760
obey the referee's decisions.

30:46.240 --> 30:47.780
The first lesson for me?

30:47.810 --> 30:49.170
So pretentious.

30:50.310 --> 30:51.030
Never mind.

30:51.310 --> 30:52.960
We're just
going through the motions anyway.

30:52.960 --> 30:54.200
The referee has finally ruled

30:54.200 --> 30:56.200
that Hongjing's No. 12, Chen Weidong,
handled the ball

30:56.200 --> 30:57.960
and awarded a penalty kick to Ning'an.

30:57.960 --> 31:00.240
Possession goes back to Ning'an.

31:02.000 --> 31:04.750
Next is a tense penalty kick.

31:05.830 --> 31:07.200
Ning'an Team's No. 14 is

31:07.200 --> 31:08.860
standing at the penalty mark.

31:10.030 --> 31:12.720
It's a test for the goalkeeper, Feng Suo.

31:27.440 --> 31:29.880
Run-up, shoot!

31:31.030 --> 31:32.110
It's in again.

31:32.110 --> 31:32.960
Two to zero.

31:32.960 --> 31:35.310
Ning'an Experimental School
extends its lead.

31:35.310 --> 31:36.880
For Hongjing No. 8 High School,

31:36.880 --> 31:38.310
this is like a blatant slap in the face.

31:38.310 --> 31:41.030
We shouldn't have come here
to embarrass ourselves!

31:41.030 --> 31:42.430
Your safety comes first.

31:46.880 --> 31:47.790
[Ning'an Experimental School 02]
[Hongjing No. 8 High School 00]

31:49.960 --> 31:52.290
Are you trying to discipline us
or save us?

31:52.310 --> 31:53.100
Sorry,

31:53.680 --> 31:55.210
we are just lousy students.

31:55.400 --> 31:56.800
Please stay away from us.

32:28.920 --> 32:31.110
They may look careless and carefree,

32:31.510 --> 32:34.170
talking like winning or losing
doesn't matter.

32:34.510 --> 32:35.920
But in fact,

32:37.150 --> 32:40.210
their faces clearly show
their unwillingness to lose,

32:40.510 --> 32:41.630
their anger,

32:42.010 --> 32:43.410
and their helplessness.

32:50.660 --> 32:52.190
Going through the motions?

32:52.760 --> 32:54.220
It doesn't look like that.

33:02.160 --> 33:03.920
Do they really not want to win?

33:03.920 --> 33:05.030
Lin Lu, are you alright?

33:05.030 --> 33:06.310
-I'm fine. Let's continue!
-Are you okay?

33:06.310 --> 33:07.240
No.

33:07.750 --> 33:09.830
These kids who say they don't care

33:10.120 --> 33:12.010
actually do care.

33:12.650 --> 33:13.980
They really want to win.

33:14.200 --> 33:16.730
They yearn for victory
more than anyone else.

33:18.790 --> 33:20.590
The fire burning in their eyes,

33:21.470 --> 33:22.960
the relentless futile efforts,

33:22.960 --> 33:25.030
yet the refusal to stop running—

33:25.790 --> 33:27.190
none of them can be faked.

33:33.730 --> 33:34.730
Do you want to win?

33:39.390 --> 33:40.230
[Receive Money by QR Code]

33:50.330 --> 33:52.650
[Receive Money by QR Code]

33:52.770 --> 33:53.190
[Loading]

33:53.270 --> 33:53.940
[Pay to Individual]

33:59.940 --> 34:01.620
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

34:02.560 --> 34:04.050
♪ Because you're with me ♪

34:06.790 --> 34:08.320
♪ The light shimmers ♪

34:09.580 --> 34:10.960
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

34:12.340 --> 34:13.750
♪ Running towards you ♪

34:14.449 --> 34:15.960
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪
